# 1. X√°c ƒë·ªãnh k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc ban ƒë·∫ßu
# Code g·ªëc chia: first_half = len // 2, second_half = ph·∫ßn c√≤n l·∫°i
# Sau ƒë√≥ gh√©p: output = second_half + first_half
total_len = len(output)
