# 2. T√°ch l·∫°i m·∫£ng output
# V√¨ output = Second + First, n√™n ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu c·ªßa list output l√† Second (d√πng key 6)
# Ph·∫ßn sau c·ªßa list output l√† First (d√πng key 5)
